sp., Douala, Cameroon, 16 Jun 1990; photographed 17 Jun; MJWC 90/204. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1309,1322,1809,1831]" pageId="29" pageNumber="330">2</emphasis>
, 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Spialia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="29" pageNumber="330" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="ploetzi" subSpecies="occidentalis">
